            "category_depth": 1,
            "languages": [
                "eng"
            ],
            "page_number": 2
        },
        "text": "Classify credit card customers as good / bad, based on information from internal and external sources. "
    },
    {
        "type": "ListItem",
        "element_id": "5eb6ec96e6a3493c1ae56747ae457b7f",
